# ğŸ¦ Bank Management System (Full-Stack Java + SQL)

A **full-stack desktop banking application** built using **Core Java, Swing UI, and MySQL database connectivity**, following industry-level development practices.  
This project simulates essential banking operations with a secure, structured, and scalable backend, aligning with a **Full-Stack Java Developer and Software Engineering mindset**.

